data.description: Where luxury meets lifestyle – welcome home! Nestled within a premium active adult gated community in Marietta, this home harmonizes upscale living with low maintenance. Strategically situated near the vibrant Marietta Square, Kennesaw Mountain National Park, and abundant shopping and dining options, this location provides seamless access to I-75. Step into this breathtaking 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence and be greeted by airy 10-foot ceilings complemented by 8-foot doors. The home’s elegance is accentuated by crown molding, designer lighting, and rich hardwood floors on the main level. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast’s dream: sparkling quartz countertops, efficient stainless-steel appliances, a sizeable island, soft-close cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, and stylish finishes, from the subway tile backsplash to the modish vent hood. The kitchen opens to an elegant dining room and a living room with a fireplace. A spacious guest room and full bathroom ensure comfort and privacy for guests. On the main floor, the primary suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, complete with walk-in closets and a spa-like bathroom featuring double sinks and a luxurious zero-entry frameless shower. Ascend to the upper level to find two additional spacious bedrooms, a bathroom, and dynamic flex space – ready to cater to your unique needs, from an office to a media room. The seller has meticulously infused this home with thoughtful upgrades, ensuring comfort and style: a whole-house dehumidifier, ambient gas logs for the fireplace, elegant glass shower doors in secondary bathrooms, and enhanced storage solutions in the laundry room and garage. Residents enjoy many amenities, including a clubhouse, refreshing pool, personal gardening plots, and direct access to Civil War trails, offering a unique blend of historical immersion and recreational activity. Embrace the ease of an HOA that cares for the yard, roof, and exterior paint, allowing you to focus on living. The cherry on top? The seller is generously offering $5,000 towards closing costs. 2172 Capers Drive is more than a house; it’s the epitome of upscale, relaxed living in Marietta!
